    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2018 luxury sedan that strikes the perfect balance between sophistication and reliability. This vehicle has been a dependable companion and remains in impressive mechanical and cosmetic shape. The exterior maintains a brilliant luster, with only minor, expected surface wear such as small stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seating is well-preserved with no cracks or thinning, and the high-resolution navigation and premium audio systems work flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, including a recent cooling system flush and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires. I have retained all service records to provide the next owner with complete peace of mind. This is a solid, turn-key vehicle that needs nothing but a new driver.",
      "price": 31500.0,
