      "description": "Presenting an expertly maintained executive vehicle that exemplifies both performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. A premier choice for those seeking a high-caliber vehicle that balances value with uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 36500.0,
