    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean, runs smooth, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car is totally ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll feel that the moment you get behind the wheel. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
